name: Kitonak
Lore: 'Natives of Kirdo III, a desert world, Kitonak possess tough, leathery skin. Many become musicians. Very patient. Thousands have been enslaved by the Empire.',
Text: 'Power +1 at a Tatooine site, or power +2 at any desert. Immune to Gravel Storm, Sandwhirl and desert landspeed requirements. Immune to attrition < the number of your musicians present.',
